### 3.2 File Routing — Next.js App Router

The `app/` directory uses file-based routing. Every `page.js` file becomes a URL. Every `route.js` file becomes an API endpoint. Here is the complete route map:

#### Public Routes (no login required)
| URL | File | Purpose |
|-----|------|---------|
| `/` | `app/page.js` | Landing page — hero, how it works, FAQ, roles |
| `/login` | `app/(auth)/login/page.js` | Login form |
| `/register` | `app/(auth)/register/page.js` | Self-registration for citizens |
| `/public-dashboard` | `app/public-dashboard/page.js` | Public stats: total issues, resolution rate |
| `/map` | `app/map/page.js` | Public interactive map of all issues |
| `/track` | `app/track/page.js` | Track complaint by Report ID (no login needed) |
| `/know-your-district` | `app/know-your-district/page.js` | Ward/zone information page |
| `/privacy-policy` | `app/privacy-policy/page.js` | Privacy policy |
| `/terms-of-service` | `app/terms-of-service/page.js` | Terms of service |
| `/issues/[id]` | `app/issues/[id]/page.js` | Public issue detail view |

#### Citizen Routes (role: CITIZEN)
| URL | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `/citizen/dashboard` | My reported issues, stats, notifications |
| `/citizen/report` | Report a new issue (full wizard with AI) |
| `/citizen/secure-dashboard` | Additional secure view |

#### Field Officer Routes (role: FIELD_OFFICER)
| URL | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `/department/dashboard` | Issues assigned to this officer's ward |
| `/department/issues` | All issues in their ward |
| `/department/resolved` | Issues they've resolved |
| `/department/stats` | Their personal performance stats |
| `/department/profile` | Profile management |

#### Department Manager Routes (role: DEPARTMENT_MANAGER)
| URL | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `/municipal/dashboard` | Department-level overview |
| `/municipal/departments` | View field officers in the department |
| `/municipal/sla-dashboard` | SLA compliance monitoring |

#### Commissioner Routes (role: MUNICIPAL_COMMISSIONER)
| URL | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `/commissioner/dashboard` | City-wide overview |
| `/commissioner/issues` | All issues across all departments |
| `/commissioner/create-staff` | Create department manager or field officer accounts |

#### Admin Routes (role: SYSTEM_ADMIN)
| URL | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `/admin/dashboard` | System-wide overview |
| `/admin/users` | User management (view, activate/deactivate) |
| `/admin/create-user` | Create any type of user |
| `/admin/departments` | Department management |
| `/admin/issues` | Full issue management |
| `/admin/analytics` | Advanced analytics |
| `/admin/reports` | Report generation |

